Name: Average resolution time for 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time elapsed for all instances of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and activity Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for cases where activity Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' for cases that are corrected and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to cases without it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time taken for a case to be resolved after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Time taken from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Request Payment' for cases that proceed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time for a case to be reopened after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' state before being approved or rejected permanently
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Time difference analysis between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to identify process bottlenecks
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Cycle time for cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to understand process efficiency
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Time until 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from the start of the case to identify early or late rejections in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
